Here‚Äôs a well-structured GitHub-friendly documentation section including **Sample**, **Structure**, and **Usage** for the `Run Once Schedule` API call in Automation Anywhere:

---

# üßæ Automation Anywhere - One-Time Bot Schedule via API

Automate your bot execution with a **one-time schedule** using Control Room's API.

---

## üìå API Endpoint

```
POST <host>/v2/schedule/automations
```

---

## üß± JSON Structure

```json
{
  "schedule": {
    "status": "ACTIVE",
    "scheduleType": "NONE",
    "timeZone": "{{TimeZone}}",
    "startDate": "{{StartDate}}",
    "startTime": "{{StartTime}}",
    "repeatEnabled": false,
    "misfireScheduleConfig": false,
    "scheduleResiliency": {
      "common": {
        "detectAndNotify": {
          "enabled": false
        },
        "recording": {
          "enabled": false,
          "botStatus": "FAILED"
        },
        "handleUnexpectedPopups": true
      }
    }
  },
  "deployment": {
    "botId": "{{MasterID}}",
    "automationName": "Testing Bot",
    "description": "Bot Created schedule for Testing bot",
    "botLabel": null,
    "automationPriority": "PRIORITY_MEDIUM",
    "inputs": {},
    "runElevated": false,
    "hideBotAgentUi": false,
    "unattendedRequest": {
      "runAsUserIds": ["{{Run_As_ID}}"],
      "poolIds": [],
      "numOfRunAsUsersToUse": "1",
      "deviceUsageType": "RUN_ONLY_ON_DEFAULT_DEVICE"
    }
  }
}
```

---

## üîç Sample Request (Filled)

```json
{
  "schedule": {
    "status": "ACTIVE",
    "scheduleType": "NONE",
    "timeZone": "Asia/Kolkata",
    "startDate": "2025-07-25",
    "startTime": "14:00:00",
    "repeatEnabled": false,
    "misfireScheduleConfig": false,
    "scheduleResiliency": {
      "common": {
        "detectAndNotify": {
          "enabled": false
        },
        "recording": {
          "enabled": false,
          "botStatus": "FAILED"
        },
        "handleUnexpectedPopups": true
      }
    }
  },
  "deployment": {
    "botId": "abc123-bot-master-id",
    "automationName": "Bot_InvoiceGenerator",
    "description": "Bot Created schedule for Bot_InvoiceGenerator",
    "botLabel": null,
    "automationPriority": "PRIORITY_MEDIUM",
    "inputs": {
      "customerName": "Tata Steel",
      "region": "South"
    },
    "runElevated": false,
    "hideBotAgentUi": false,
    "unattendedRequest": {
      "runAsUserIds": ["def456-runner-id"],
      "poolIds": [],
      "numOfRunAsUsersToUse": "1",
      "deviceUsageType": "RUN_ONLY_ON_DEFAULT_DEVICE"
    }
  }
}
```


## ‚úÖ Tips

* `scheduleType: NONE` = One-time schedule.
* `repeatEnabled: false` disables recurrence.
* Use `Asia/Kolkata` or your desired IANA-compliant time zone.
* Use `inputs` to send dynamic parameters if your bot uses variables.

